00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,240
Thank you, Brother Yang.

277
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:49,660
I should thank you.

278
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:53,030
Thank you for supporting me all the time.

279
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,200
Here.

280
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:06,990
Don't be too worried.

281
00:17:07,609 --> 00:17:09,190
We'll get through this together.

282
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,790
We've gone so far.

283
00:17:13,569 --> 00:17:14,819
We're close to victory.

284
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,430
I'll always be with you.

285
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,570
Brother Yang.

286
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:44,140
Are you doing the accounts?

287
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:48,740
Yes, we don't have much time left.

288
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,580
We can hardly earn enough money.

289
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,730
Look at the turnover. I haven't subtracted the cost.

290
00:17:55,710 --> 00:17:58,720
Brother Yang, don't worry.

291
00:17:59,930 --> 00:18:02,250
Have you ever heard of the Universe Principle?

292
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:06,410
If we believe we can make it, we will make it.

293
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:17,730
We will make it.

294
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:21,400
Don't worry. I'll always be with you.

295
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,230
Understand?

296
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:30,230
You're the best.

297
00:18:38,020 --> 00:18:38,270
Hey.

298
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:40,670
-Uh.
-Qi'er.

299
00:18:41,490 --> 00:18:42,770
Is Bojji on leave today?

300
00:18:43,410 --> 00:18:45,620
Yes.

301
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:50,400
Do you know what happened to Bojji recently?

302
00:18:51,290 --> 00:18:51,980
It seems

303
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:55,590
she has encountered some problems.

304
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:59,370
No, no.

305
00:19:01,390 --> 00:19:02,810
She is doing okay.

306
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:04,780
Everything is fine.

307
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:19,890
Fine, I can tell you.

308
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:22,260
Well.

309
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:27,590
Her father had an emergency and was sent to the hospital so she needs 500,000 baht to pay for the hospital bills.

310
00:19:27,710 --> 00:19:30,190
But she doesn't have so much money so she's been very anxious recently.

311
00:19:30,410 --> 00:19:34,910
She really doesn't know where to get so much money.

312
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:38,410
I heard she planned to turn to an unofficial loan.

313
00:19:39,690 --> 00:19:42,220
She wouldn't let me tell you.

314
00:19:45,520 --> 00:19:47,140
-I'm also anxious.
-Qi'er.

315
00:19:47,710 --> 00:19:49,900
This is such big news. Why didn't you tell me earlier?

316
00:19:51,090 --> 00:19:58,770
She said you had a lot to deal with. She doesn't want you to be more worried.

317
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:02,870
She didn't want to ask you to help her.

318
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:06,390
Don't tell her I told you the news.

319
00:20:23,350 --> 00:20:24,870
I'll help Bojji pay the medical bills.

320
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:26,970
Are you sure?

321
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:30,550
Not now.

322
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:33,620
But if necessary, I'll lend money to her first.

323
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,190
But it's been almost three months since we promised the creditor.

324
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:38,770
If you help Bojji now,

325
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:44,980
where can you get enough money to pay the debt?

326
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,810
But Bojji is one of our staff.

327
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,670
But I have the most shares in Little Sun.

328
00:20:52,780 --> 00:20:54,670
I won't allow you to lend your money to Bojji.

329
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:59,020
-But...
-Bojji works for us.

330
00:21:00,430 --> 00:21:02,640
As the biggest shareholder of Little Sun,

331
00:21:03,690 --> 00:21:04,940
I have the responsibility to help her.

332
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:07,340
Brother Yang.

333
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:10,750
Don't worry.

334
00:21:12,950 --> 00:21:14,230
Let me handle this.

335
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:41,940
Bojji.

336
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:52,140
Give back my money.

337
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,040
No need to count.

338
00:22:09,850 --> 00:22:10,200
It's not enough.

339
00:22:11,340 --> 00:22:12,210
We're still short of 200,000 yuan.

340
00:22:14,820 --> 00:22:15,640
What?

341
00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:18,510
You said you would pay off the debt within three months.

342
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:20,900
If you can't pay back all the money now, I'll capture all of you.

343
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,420
Go!

344
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:28,520
-Oh my god.
-Wait.

345
00:22:30,780 --> 00:22:31,140
Hey.

346
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:32,990
It's you again.

347
00:22:35,410 --> 00:22:36,460
Please wait a while.

348
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:43,750
Brother Yang.

349
00:22:57,860 --> 00:22:58,330
Brother Yang.

350
00:22:59,530 --> 00:23:01,670
Do you remember what I said to you?

351
00:23:11,130 --> 00:23:12,030
Brother Yang.

352
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:15,110
Actually, I have some savings.

353
00:23:16,250 --> 00:23:19,910
-My parents opened that account for me.
-That's your money.

354
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,880
I can't use it to solve my problem.

355
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:24,380
But...

356
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:26,930
I really can't use your money.

357
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:33,190
But you've already used it to help Bojji.

358
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:36,110
If we are only short of 200,000 baht,

359
00:23:36,810 --> 00:23:38,080
I should have that much.

360
00:23:38,690 --> 00:23:39,670
Phumjai.

361
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:42,250
I said I really couldn't use your money.

362
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:44,990
But you have no other choice now, Brother Yang.

363
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:48,160
Brother Yang.

364
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:50,020
I understand

365
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,070
when it comes to the money problem,

366
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:54,320
no matter how much money you need, you don't want to bother others.

367
00:23:55,390 --> 00:23:58,200
But now we really have no other choice.

368
00:23:59,650 --> 00:24:01,110
Let me help you, please.

369
00:24:10,040 --> 00:24:10,770
Then...

370
00:24:12,390 --> 00:24:14,330
You just think of it as my money to buy your shares in Little Sun.

371
00:24:16,570 --> 00:24:17,200
What shares?

372
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:22,870
I didn't give you enough money to get the shares in Little Sun.

373
00:24:24,890 --> 00:24:27,860
So you're not using my money. It's yours.

374
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:30,050
Deal.

375
00:24:31,320 --> 00:24:32,780
Phumjai has 50 percent of the total shares.

376
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:35,390
Mr. Yang has 49 percent of the total shares.

377
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:38,420
Though Phumjai has more shares,

378
00:24:38,840 --> 00:24:41,100
Mr. Yang has the final say on the decision related to the shop.

379
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:42,800
Because he's a discretionary investor.

380
00:24:45,810 --> 00:24:46,250
Brother Yang.

381
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,360
You can take my 200,000 baht

382
00:24:50,020 --> 00:24:50,830
as

383
00:24:52,360 --> 00:24:53,380
my investment in our shop.

384
00:24:53,910 --> 00:24:55,270
So that our shop will do better.

385
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:00,170
Let's be partners.

386
00:25:01,060 --> 00:25:02,880
We should've done it in the beginning, right?

387
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:07,990
Okay, Brother Yang?

388
00:25:08,850 --> 00:25:10,090
Let me help you, Brother Yang.

389
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:10,880
Okay?

390
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:16,110
Okay.

391
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:17,740
I'll accept it.

392
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:30,110
Enjoy the food, sir.

393
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:33,340
I'll get you more if you need. There's no hurry.

394
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:38,140
I'll get you another two, or three, or four if you need.

395
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,000
Let him out.

396
00:26:02,130 --> 00:26:03,590
Guys, it's Phojai's voice.

397
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,610
What's wrong, Boss No.2?

398
00:26:13,670 --> 00:26:16,680
Nothing. I slept for too long and got some cramps.

399
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:22,760
-Hey.
-It's all settled, right?

400
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,710
Yes.

401
00:26:23,830 --> 00:26:24,130
Okay.

402
00:26:33,740 --> 00:26:34,720
How are you, Phojai?

403
00:26:35,330 --> 00:26:36,360
Are you hurt?

404
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,460
Are you okay, Phojai?

405
00:26:39,950 --> 00:26:40,370
I'm fine.

406
00:26:41,050 --> 00:26:41,670
Really.

407
00:26:42,850 --> 00:26:43,640
Wait.

408
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:47,700
I heard him call you Boss No.2

409
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,440
or something else.

410
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:52,520
What is it? Did I mishear?

411
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,150
Well...

412
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,080
How could you let my competitors know our information?

413
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:03,820
What should I do now? Tell me.

414
00:27:04,260 --> 00:27:06,220
Have you thought about it? Tell me.

415
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:07,190
Tell me.

416
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:11,680
I can help you.

417
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,440
To be honest,

418
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:24,430
But for you, my company would have collapsed.

419
00:27:28,300 --> 00:27:28,700
Oh.

420
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,280
Thank you very much.

421
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:37,800
Too heavy for you?

422
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:40,810
You're so weak.

423
00:27:40,810 --> 00:27:41,660
Come on.

424
00:27:43,210 --> 00:27:45,010
I don't carry it every day like Boss No.2.

425
00:27:46,450 --> 00:27:48,260
Look at his muscles.

426
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:55,710
I was so worried about you.

427
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:56,810
I shouldn't have been worried.

428
00:27:57,000 --> 00:28:00,000
Forget it. Guys, since Phojai has come back safely,

429
00:28:00,230 --> 00:28:02,700
let's celebrate it. What do you guys want to eat?

430
00:28:03,210 --> 00:28:06,460
Let me be the sponsor for your food this time.

431
00:28:06,930 --> 00:28:08,250
The sponsor, yes.

432
00:28:08,930 --> 00:28:11,200
I'll be the sponsor, yes.

433
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:12,280
What do you guys want to eat?

434
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:15,800
Qi'er, do you want to eat hot pot?

435
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:20,280
Phumjai, what would you like to eat?

436
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:23,340
Cheers!

437
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:27,580
So delicious.

438
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:28,280
Brother.

439
00:28:29,930 --> 00:28:31,440
Thank you.

440
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:37,620
Great.

441
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:41,170
Guys,

442
00:28:41,970 --> 00:28:44,570
there will be some changes about Little Sun.

443
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:48,630
We have an announcement to make.

444
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,710
Let me say thanks to all of you

445
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:56,540
for your hard work at Little Sun these days.

446
00:28:57,450 --> 00:29:00,420
I don't know how to repay you for what you've done for Little Sun.

447
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:04,060
So I've decided

448
00:29:05,210 --> 00:29:06,690
to give all my shares

449
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:08,210
to all of you.

450
00:29:10,330 --> 00:29:11,030
Really?

451
00:29:12,180 --> 00:29:13,840
The shares of Little Sun?

452
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:20,070
You are so nice, boss. I'm so happy! I'm going to be a boss!

453
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:22,690
Oh, boss, Phumjai.

454
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:24,790
I don't think I should accept it.

455
00:29:25,180 --> 00:29:26,740
Give the shares to them.

456
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:31,510
You helped me a lot. I don't know how to repay you and Phumjai.

457
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:33,590
Bojji.

458
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:35,270
You don't have to give me the shares.

459
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:39,430
I think that's too much for me.

460
00:29:40,750 --> 00:29:41,930
Just take it, Tag.

461
00:29:43,050 --> 00:29:44,730
You deserve to have your own business.

462
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:46,440
Consider it

463
00:29:47,210 --> 00:29:48,820
as a gift from me.

464
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,020
Thank you, Phumjai.

465
00:29:51,780 --> 00:29:52,920
Thank you, Brother Yang.

466
00:29:55,150 --> 00:29:57,210
You don't need to give shares to me.

467
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:59,790
I'm already very busy with my own work.

468
00:30:01,190 --> 00:30:02,290
Me too, Yang.

469
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:05,220
Give your shares to them. They want to have their own business.

470
00:30:06,910 --> 00:30:10,760
But boss, your shares left...

471
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:14,270
Yes.

472
00:30:18,940 --> 00:30:19,480
It’s okay.

473
00:30:20,970 --> 00:30:21,720
He is the real boss now.

474
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,330
And we

475
00:30:29,450 --> 00:30:29,780
Oh?

476
00:30:29,840 --> 00:30:32,160
have another announcement to make.

477
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:33,420
Really?

478
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:39,050
We're going to take three days off next week.

479
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:42,680
I've been waiting for it.

480
00:30:49,580 --> 00:30:51,330
Guys, it's here.

481
00:30:51,330 --> 00:30:52,370
Let's go.

482
00:30:52,870 --> 00:30:54,470
Let's go.

483
00:30:54,740 --> 00:31:00,400
Hello, mountains. We're from Little Sun.

484
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,500
Bojji, we've arrived. We've arrived, guys.

485
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:03,890
Come and get your luggage.

486
00:31:03,890 --> 00:31:04,720
Okay.

487
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:07,670
Come with me.

488
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:13,410
I'm familiar with this place.

489
00:31:13,410 --> 00:31:15,100
Brother Yang, come with me.

490
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:21,860
Phojai.

491
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,350
Are these all yours?

492
00:31:26,420 --> 00:31:28,230
We'll stay here for only three days. Why did you pack so much luggage?

493
00:31:28,860 --> 00:31:30,200
Are you moving?

494
00:31:31,430 --> 00:31:32,300
Yes, I'm moving.

495
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:34,220
To where?

496
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:37,800
You told me you wanted me to move in with you, right?

497
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:39,800
So...

498
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:43,790
I'll move into your apartment after this trip.

499
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:45,500
Really?

500
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:47,000
Of course.

501
00:31:47,170 --> 00:31:48,030
Are you serious, Phojai?

502
00:31:48,030 --> 00:31:48,810
Yes.

503
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:52,060
I love you.

504
00:31:57,990 --> 00:31:58,700
I love you too.

505
00:31:59,090 --> 00:31:59,830
Okay.

506
00:32:02,870 --> 00:32:03,890
-Let's go.
-Okay.

507
00:32:19,570 --> 00:32:20,690
Guys, cheers!

508
00:32:20,690 --> 00:32:21,610
Cheers!

509
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:26,020
Little Sun, oh yeah.

510
00:32:27,120 --> 00:32:30,860
Guys, a friend of mine opened this new restaurant.

511
00:32:32,040 --> 00:32:34,150
The shrimps are very delicious.

512
00:32:38,230 --> 00:32:42,510
I want someone to shell a shrimp for me.

513
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,960
It's a difficult job.

514
00:32:45,090 --> 00:32:47,450
I also want someone to shell a shrimp for me.

515
00:32:47,450 --> 00:32:48,590
You want the shrimp, right?

516
00:32:49,010 --> 00:32:51,180
Okay, I'll shell one for you.

517
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,280
Here you are, Bojji.

518
00:32:54,570 --> 00:32:56,060
Thank you.

519
00:32:56,060 --> 00:32:57,770
Are you messing with me?

520
00:32:57,770 --> 00:32:58,660
You went too far.

521
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:00,760
It's fun.

522
00:33:03,430 --> 00:33:05,340
Open your mouth, Bojji. Let's share it.

523
00:33:06,990 --> 00:33:08,000
Do you want this, Phojai?

524
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:08,790
Yes.

525
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,300
Help yourselves.

526
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:17,680
I'll be right back.

527
00:33:24,890 --> 00:33:27,670
Hi, son. How have you been?

528
00:33:28,010 --> 00:33:30,530
I'm doing well here. Mom, you don't need to worry about me.

529
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:33,280
When will you come back?

530
00:33:34,990 --> 00:33:37,040
I need to take care of my business here.

531
00:33:37,330 --> 00:33:41,210
I can't go back now. But I'll be able to see you soon.

532
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,730
Okay.

533
00:33:43,710 --> 00:33:45,080
Take care.

534
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:46,320
Okay.

535
00:33:46,810 --> 00:33:47,240
Bye.

536
00:33:55,890 --> 00:33:56,600
Nice shot!

537
00:33:59,850 --> 00:34:02,780
Yeah. See? I did a lot better this time.

538
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:04,980
Yes.

539
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:09,699
You caught every ball I threw.

540
00:34:11,530 --> 00:34:11,960
Well done.

541
00:34:18,770 --> 00:34:19,320
Good job.

542
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,570
Good. Good.

543
00:34:24,639 --> 00:34:25,330
Hey, you dropped the ball.

544
00:34:32,210 --> 00:34:32,780
Nice shot!

545
00:34:32,780 --> 00:34:33,460
Are you tired?

546
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:35,300
One last shot. Come on.

547
00:34:39,409 --> 00:34:40,860
Let's take a break.

548
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,430
Brother Yang.

549
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:02,860
Do you know, I used to sit and wonder

550
00:35:03,970 --> 00:35:05,690
when I started liking you?

551
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:09,800
But I can't figure it out.

552
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:11,580
Oh.

553
00:35:13,470 --> 00:35:14,330
But you know what?

554
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,810
Whenever something good happens to me,

