00:57:11,920 --> 00:57:12,870
Lian Lian Bu Dong.

856
00:57:13,440 --> 00:57:14,820
Love in Translation.

857
00:57:15,100 --> 00:57:16,630
Author: Tammy.

858
00:57:17,040 --> 00:57:18,590
She wrote it herself?

859
00:57:19,290 --> 00:57:20,930
