872
00:58:13,940 --> 00:58:16,900
By then, we'll probably have our hands full.

873
00:58:21,180 --> 00:58:23,520
I'll take a look over there and see if I can help with anything.

874
00:58:24,900 --> 00:58:26,010
Wait.

875
00:58:30,840 --> 00:58:31,730
What's wrong?

876
00:58:36,720 --> 00:58:38,000
Do you have something to tell me?

877
00:58:41,100 --> 00:58:41,670
Well,

878
00:58:43,430 --> 00:58:45,330
