879
00:58:47,380 --> 00:58:48,920
I have something to tell you.

880
00:58:50,600 --> 00:58:50,920
Hmm?

881
00:59:07,080 --> 00:59:08,740
You know what that means, right?

882
00:59:15,560 --> 00:59:17,110
Brother Yang, this number...

883
00:59:18,920 --> 00:59:20,230
This is what I want to tell you.

884
00:59:23,350 --> 00:59:24,060
I love you.

885
00:59:25,410 --> 00:59:27,490
For life.

886
00:59:30,080 --> 00:59:31,600
I love you forever.

887
00:59:38,790 --> 00:59:39,490
Phumjai.

888
00:59:41,520 --> 00:59:42,520
From now on,

889
00:59:44,090 --> 00:59:45,460
besides being business partners,

890
00:59:47,900 --> 00:59:48,640
can we

891
00:59:50,420 --> 00:59:52,150
also be life partners?

892
01:00:09,950 --> 01:00:10,890
That's my answer.

893
01:00:13,820 --> 01:00:16,160
I'll be with you forever.

894
01:00:17,450 --> 01:00:18,150
I

895
01:00:19,040 --> 01:00:19,640
want to be with you.

