01:00:37,050 --> 01:00:38,030
I have something for you.

897
01:00:39,120 --> 01:00:39,830
What is it?

898
01:00:48,800 --> 01:00:50,920
This is the ring my dad gave to my mom.

899
01:00:55,420 --> 01:00:55,800
This...

