01:00:56,780 --> 01:00:59,910
It's so precious. I'm afraid I'll lose it Brother Yang.

901
01:01:02,730 --> 01:01:03,530
I trust you.

902
01:01:05,060 --> 01:01:07,350
You won't lose it, right?

903
01:01:36,520 --> 01:01:37,010
But

904
01:01:37,960 --> 01:01:39,500
I have nothing for you.

905
01:01:40,990 --> 01:01:42,960
You've given me enough.

906
01:02:08,910 --> 01:02:10,290
You're my life partner now.

907
01:02:11,250 --> 01:02:13,260
I won't let you withdraw easily.

908
01:02:16,800 --> 01:02:18,260
I don't plan to withdraw.

909
01:02:35,470 --> 01:02:36,740
I'm the happiest I've ever been.

