923
01:04:18,250 --> 01:04:19,240
I see.

924
01:04:20,040 --> 01:04:22,350
Do you have friends there?

925
01:04:25,370 --> 01:04:26,020
Yes.

926
01:04:27,170 --> 01:04:28,120
There was a kid.

927
01:04:29,660 --> 01:04:32,220
