928
01:04:33,100 --> 01:04:34,810
Did you speak Thai then?

929
01:04:35,460 --> 01:04:37,480
Then how did you communicate with him?

930
01:04:39,500 --> 01:04:40,840
You know, talking without knowing the language.

931
01:04:45,820 --> 01:04:46,720
I even took a photo.

932
01:04:49,390 --> 01:04:49,690
What?

933
01:04:52,420 --> 01:04:53,300
Brother Yang.

934
01:04:54,220 --> 01:04:55,220
That's my photo.

935
01:05:02,690 --> 01:05:03,150
Here.

936
01:05:12,560 --> 01:05:14,020
Why can't I remember you?

937
01:05:16,000 --> 01:05:16,760
It's not strange at all.

938
01:05:17,730 --> 01:05:18,680
I was young back then.

939
01:05:20,060 --> 01:05:21,330
But whether you remember it or not,

940
01:05:22,310 --> 01:05:23,460
you're with me now.

941
01:05:25,640 --> 01:05:26,240
You're right.

942
01:05:28,000 --> 01:05:28,800
Tell me.

943
01:05:29,810 --> 01:05:30,760
The two of us

944
01:05:32,150 --> 01:05:34,180
