945
01:05:36,120 --> 01:05:36,940
Do you still believe that?

946
01:05:37,370 --> 01:05:37,810
Yes.

947
01:05:38,830 --> 01:05:39,800
Don't you, Brother Yang?

948
01:05:42,230 --> 01:05:42,870
In the past,

949
01:05:44,020 --> 01:05:44,830
I didn't believe it.

950
01:05:47,770 --> 01:05:48,430
But now,

951
01:05:51,650 --> 01:05:52,260
I believe it.

952
01:06:16,060 --> 01:06:18,950
Even though we don't know if we will succeed,

953
01:06:19,810 --> 01:06:21,330
Start a business together.

