976
01:07:23,550 --> 01:07:24,240
Just like you.

977
01:07:25,100 --> 01:07:26,150
Who wouldn't like you?

978
01:07:26,980 --> 01:07:28,140
As if to emphasize to us

979
01:07:28,720 --> 01:07:31,530
